 {"question": "Can a small team implement Conga CPQ without consultants?", "answer": "This is not recommended. Conga CPQ's configuration depth requires expertise that takes months to develop. Most successful implementations involve Conga's professional services team or certified partners. Attempting a self-service implementation with a complex product catalog typically leads to suboptimal configuration, user frustration, and a second engagement with consultants to fix the problems. Budget for professional help from the start."},
